org.osgeo.mapguide

Class MgServerInformationProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgServerInformationProperties

  • public class MgServerInformationProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    ServerAdmin properties. Note that this is not a complete list of the properties which may be set for a server. Values stored in the server's config file are also properties of the server. These properties are defined in MgConfigProperties.h.
